How to run frontend app, using apache which is a software inside a m/c
set port no. 80 to run the app in aws security group
Automating the process of building and deploying: Code > create Artifacts > store artifacts > deploy infra
Load Balancer in routing traffic and to communicate bwn them
Containers and docker 
We need container to run the apps and its process as apache java-jar
If there is no app no need of container too
Running sample container , docker run <Image>
to export to outer world, docker run -p 80:80 <image>
